headline: 3 Reasons BEN is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Since May 2025, Franklin Resources has been in a holding pattern, posting a small return of 0.7% while floating around $22.36. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 13.1% gain during that period.
